## Debugging

### Verbose Generation
```bash
penguiflow generate --spec {{ agent_name }}.yaml --verbose
```

### Check Generated Code Syntax
```bash
python -m py_compile src/{{ package_name }}/tools/*.py
```

### Run Single Tool Test
```bash
uv run pytest tests/test_tools/test_my_tool.py -v
```
